                <li>Does not generate cluster content</li>
                <li>You need writers or Surfer AI credits</li>
                <li>Pro features behind $219/mo paywall</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams that want optimization quality over cluster volume.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/surfer-seo/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">04</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
