            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Affiliate bloggers comfortable with the detection risk.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/koala-ai/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">05</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Scalenut</div>
