                <li>Focused on long-form 1,500–5,000+ word articles</li>
                <li>WordPress + Shopify auto-publish</li>
                <li>Built-in AI detection tool inside the editor</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>$249/mo monthly — 5x Machined's entry price</li>
                <li>"Undetectable" claims disputed by independent tests</li>
                <li>No cluster approach like Machined</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams paying premium for long-form with Shopify integration.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/scalenut/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
