          </div>
          <div class="migration-step">
            <div>
              <span class="time">15 min</span>
              <h4>Cancel Machined</h4>
              <p>Machined is monthly. Cancel from Account → Billing. Published content stays on your CMS — you only lose access to the generation pipeline.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
